## Live tweaks during the demo

Because everything is plain HTML + CSS vars, you can tweak things live in devtools:

- **Swap theme** — button in the floating pill, or `html[data-theme="<name>"]`.
- **Change accent color** — edit `--accent` in the active `html[data-theme]` block of `css/styles.css`.
- **Edit copy** — every `<h1>`, `<p>`, button label is just text in the HTML.

